The example RICE 3.x application exist of the following files:

 - simple3x.c                   source file (pure ANSI-C)
 - rice.cod (:= simple3x.cod)   RICE code-file
 - rice.lnk (:= simple3x.lnk)   RICE link-file

For testing you can use the knowledge base ANIMALS.KB or one of your own.
See the file RICE3X.DOC for more info on updating RICE 3.x applications
and the file RICE.DOC for more info on RICE itself.

